data.description: New Construction without the wait!! This beautiful 3 bed 2.5 bath home has a large fully fenced yard with flowers and garden space. Spacious light-filled, open-concept living area, perfect for entertaining. Functional kitchen with ample cabinet space, quartz countertops, & new stainless steel appliances. Primary bedroom with walk-in closet & bathroom attached. The downstairs offers an additional living space and flex room. Enjoy the community's heated pool, beachfront access & more. Enjoy access to private Hood Canal waterfront park, swimming pool, clubhouse & playground. Fully enjoy the PNW lifestyle--kayaking, clamming, hiking/ORV trails nearby, and DNR land. Easy commute to PSNS/Seattle ferry or Amazon. This house is ready for you!
